					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">If you want a mapper you can easily obtain, the most obvious choice would be the MMC3.
<br />In my opinion, you SHOULD get your program/game/demo to work on the real thing. There are plenty of people here with devcarts that can test it for you; if someone isn't available for whatever reason, most of the current 'good' NES emulators behave closely enough to the real thing (especially Nintendulator, which was designed for this sole purpose) to give you a general idea of whether it will work or not.</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Quietust, QMT Productions
<br />P.S. If you don't get this note, let me know and I'll write you another.</div>
